    <text class="block intro-txt">
      I am an Engineer focused on digital user experiences.
    </text>
    <text class="block intro-txt">
      My hobbies and passions include User Experience, Web Development and Photography. My goal is to solve problems through thoughtful ideas.
    </text>
    <text class="block intro-txt">
      Connect with me on <text class="">Wechat : yuexiadeshenma</text>
    </text>
  </view>
</view>
